Holotype .
SAMA R65030 (Field number
SJR 10954
), adult male, Muller Range , Gugusu Camp , Western Province , Papua New Guinea ( 5.729°S , 142.263°E ;
515 m a.s.l.
), collected by Stephen Richards and Chris Dahl on
